        "content": "<p>ricochet opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13666\">PR #13666</a> from <code>ricochet:worktree-resource-implements</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This wires up resource support in <code>bindgen!</code>'s <code>named_imports</code></p>\n<p>For named imports every host method takes an extra embedder-chosen <code>id</code><br>\nso the host can tell which matched import a call came through.<br>\nThe opaque marker type is reused from the sibling interface-import module<br>\nvia a <code>pub use</code>, so <code>Resource&lt;T&gt;</code> values are shared across both paths.</p>\n<p>All the new code paths only fire when an <code>id</code> is present.</p>\n<p>Follow on to changes made in #13513</p>\n</blockquote>",
